<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨٠- قالَ بَصُرْتُ بِما لَمْ يَبْصُرُوا بِهِ فَقَبَضْتُ قَبْضَةً مِنْ أَثَرِ الرَّسُولِ فَنَبَذْتُها وَكَذلِكَ سَوَّلَتْ لِي نَفْسِي <span class="c2">(٩٦)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٨١- أَلَمْ تَرَ أَنَّ اللَّهَ يُزْجِي سَحاباً ثُمَّ يُؤَلِّفُ بَيْنَهُ ثُمَّ يَجْعَلُهُ رُكاماً فَتَرَى الْوَدْقَ يَخْرُجُ مِنْ خِلالِهِ وَيُنَزِّلُ مِنَ السَّماءِ مِنْ جِبالٍ فِيها مِنْ بَرَدٍ فَيُصِيبُ بِهِ مَنْ يَشاءُ وَيَصْرِفُهُ عَنْ مَنْ يَشاءُ يَكادُ سَنا بَرْقِهِ يَذْهَبُ بِالْأَبْصارِ <span class="c2">(٤٣)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يُقَلِّبُ اللَّهُ اللَّيْلَ وَالنَّهارَ إِنَّ فِي ذلِكَ لَعِبْرَةً لِأُولِي الْأَبْصارِ <span class="c2">(٤٤)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٨٢- وَما يَسْتَوِي الْأَعْمى وَالْبَصِيرُ <span class="c2">(١٩)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَلَا الظُّلُماتُ وَلَا النُّورُ <span class="c2">(٢٠)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلَا الظِّلُّ وَلَا الْحَرُورُ <span class="c2">(٢١)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَما يَسْتَوِي الْأَحْياءُ وَلَا الْأَمْواتُ إِنَّ اللَّهَ يُسْمِعُ مَنْ يَشاءُ وَما أَنْتَ بِمُسْمِعٍ مَنْ فِي الْقُبُورِ <span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٨٣- وَأَبْصِرْهُمْ فَسَوْفَ يُبْصِرُونَ <span class="c2">(١٧٥)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَفَبِعَذابِنا يَسْتَعْجِلُونَ <span class="c2">(١٧٦)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَإِذا نَزَلَ بِساحَتِهِمْ فَساءَ صَباحُ الْمُنْذَرِينَ <span class="c2">(١٧٧)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَتَوَلَّ عَنْهُمْ حَتَّى حِينٍ <span class="c2">(١٧٨)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَأَبْصِرْ فَسَوْفَ يُبْصِرُونَ <span class="c2">(١٧٩)</span> <span class="c2">«٤»</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٨٤- وَاذْكُرْ عِبادَنا إِبْراهِيمَ وَإِسْحاقَ وَيَعْقُوبَ أُولِي الْأَيْدِي وَالْأَبْصارِ <span class="c2">(٤٥)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>إِنَّا أَخْلَصْناهُمْ بِخالِصَةٍ ذِكْرَى الدَّارِ <span class="c2">(٤٦)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَإِنَّهُمْ عِنْدَنا لَمِنَ الْمُصْطَفَيْنَ الْأَخْيارِ <span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> <span class="c2">«٥»</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٨٥- وَما يَسْتَوِي الْأَعْمى وَالْبَصِيرُ وَالَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحاتِ وَلَا الْمُسِيءُ قَلِيلًا ما تَتَذَكَّرُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٨)</span> <span class="c2">«٦»</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٨٦- وَلَقَدْ رَآهُ نَزْلَةً أُخْرى <span class="c2">(١٣)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>عِنْدَ سِدْرَةِ الْمُنْتَهى <span class="c2">(١٤)</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>عِنْدَها جَنَّةُ الْمَأْوى <span class="c2">(١٥)</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>إِذْ يَغْشَى السِّدْرَةَ ما يَغْشى <span class="c2">(١٦)</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>ما زاغَ الْبَصَرُ وَما طَغى <span class="c2">(١٧)</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>لَقَدْ رَأى مِنْ آياتِ رَبِّهِ الْكُبْرى <span class="c2">(١٨)</span> <span class="c2">«٧»</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>٨٧- وَإِنَّ لَكَ لَأَجْراً غَيْرَ مَمْنُونٍ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>وَإِنَّكَ لَعَلى خُلُقٍ عَظِيمٍ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>فَسَتُبْصِرُ وَيُبْصِرُونَ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>بِأَيِّكُمُ الْمَفْتُونُ <span class="c2">(٦)</span> <span class="c2">«٨»</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>٨٨- يُنَبَّؤُا الْإِنْسانُ يَوْمَئِذٍ بِما قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ <span class="c2">(١٣)</span><a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>بَلِ الْإِنْسانُ عَلى نَفْسِهِ بَصِيرَةٌ <span class="c2">(١٤)</span><a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>وَلَوْ أَلْقى مَعاذِيرَهُ <span class="c2">(١٥)</span> <span class="c2">«٩»</span><a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
